data.description: Many upgrades in this customized home in the well located Monterra subdivision in Minden.  Spacious entry area leads to great room with high ceilings.  Hand built custom media center/bookshelf in living room is included in the sale.  Kitchen is bordered by two breakfast bars offering the utmost in social interaction.  There are plenty of granite counters and cabinets, all enhanced by stylish small tile back splash. Primary bedroom is large with shower and jetted tub, huge walk in closet, and double sinks.  Two more bedrooms and a bath are at the other end of the house.  Upstairs is a Bonus Room of 364 sq.ft. room can be bedroom or workout room with its own full bath and thermostat control - included in Square Footage.    Outside there are two paver patio areas, one with BBQ gas line.  Green house, berry bushes, peach and mulberry trees, many perennial flowers, gate access on both sides of the house and a wildflower garden offer aesthetic beauty with minimal maintenance.  Back yard also has a french drain one each side running to the front of the property.   Home inspection is on hand - done 12.18 by Parodi Home Inspection. There were a few minor repairs that will be taken care of after the holidays. AS-IS Sale.   Original owner is licensed real estate agent.  Seller may require short rent back after the close of escrow.    A gorgeous home with a very livable floorplan.
